column3: A bunch of crabs appear to nip at you with their sharp pincers!
So...this dude kinda sucks.
Yucky slime! Hurry, defeat it before it drools all over you!
A vermin from Hell. And it has a giant hammer?!
This is literally a give me. Do you really want to lose to a potted plant?
Since when could frogs fly?!
It's just you and Mr.Bones. What kind of misery is this?
Wow. So you're really going to beat up a dog? Some hero you are.
Jello and numbers? It reminds you of the those miserable nights studying for class.
For some reason the work Jockey comes to mind...
His grubby little hands frighten you.
Harps with wings descend upon you. Luring you in with their nostalgic sounds.
A sad horse walking with his head down (literally) in sadness. Might as well kill it.
A speedy snail with a shell sharp as a theifs freshly sharpened daggers.
Its mouth dribbles with puke as it repeatedly says Puka Puka!
Oh no. What kind of legal trouble did you get into this time?
A weird hybrid between a platypus and a manitcore named...Perry?
The room is just occupied by some dude that wont shut up.
A fierce female warrior weilding a glowing lasso!
A slimy creature that keeps lunging toward your face!
A gazebo sits alone in the room. Pure stone, yet you feel its gaze...
Ha! I bet you wish had a ghoulfriend you loser.
Wow um. Good luck?
The nose immediately snaps towards your direction due to your stench!
He has no special powers, but he just really hates you.
A foot bigger than the biggest foot of Footfeetbigger Land!
A vampire with fangs so tiny he can't bite anything.
GET THAT TONGUE AWAY FROM ME WEIRDO!
This man wont shut up about the amazing health coverage his agency offers.
This stone golem looks a little...stoned?
You open the door to an pitch black room. Several tentacles come at you, pulling you in!
Will not pursue anyone of Level 3 or below. Otherwise, it lunges at you with a piercing scream!
Will not pursue anyone of Level 3 or below. Otherwise, they launch towards you in their impressive aircraft!
Will not pursue anyone of Level 3 or below. Otherwise, face the judgement of his highness,
Will not pursue anyone of Level 4 or below. Otherwise, its girthy tentacles detain you. Break free!
Will not pursue anyone of Level 4 or below. Otherwise, fight for your life. Or live as a shadow in his underworld.
Will not pursue anyone of Level 5 or below. Otherwise, fight for glory, wealth, and well...to stay alive!
